Modified original to my needs and fixed a little bug.

Tasks:

  - mmd2tex:    compile all .mmd files down to .tex files
  - tex2pdf:    compile the main .tex file down to a .pdf (see below)
  - openreader: opens the generated .pdf file in a reader
  - clean:      cleans up temporary files
  - default:    [mmd2tex, tex2pdf, tex2pdfclean]

Variables:

  - FileName: The name of the main TeX file;
